{"tid":1402941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講曬，hit and run，有冇前線同出黎發夢嘅人唔同意","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:19:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:42:42.000Z","uid":42943,"like":421,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"937108f08ed3249b641332fb449ff7b5436dfd0d","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"我唔想再見到有手足比人拉。<br />\n<br />\n見唔見到早兩晚馬鞍山 hit and run 幾咁成功啊？<br />\n<br />\n留守對峙係作用唔大，仲會有手足比人拉。<br />\n<br />\n今日搞完尖沙咀狗屋，收到風有狗黎就應該走，唔一定散水，可以係轉場轉目標啊。<br />\n<br />\n你地見唔見到幾多出黎做支援嘅女仔比人拉啊，你班撚樣！<br />\n<br />\n今日見到有幾架車狗著黑衫扮同路人，我就更加肯定前線係有鬼！<br />\n<br />\n我今日都有走到前線，但我唔敢屌大家。我聽日一定再上去同前線講，屌到你地開花！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-唔需要set時間幾時走，睇情況，睇scout報料<br />\n-有50狗以上即轉場<br />\n-拉想守嘅手足走<br />\n-有必要時會打鳩堅持留嘅人<br />\n<br />\n咪撚再守啊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Hit and Run </span><br />\n<br />\n正皮- hit and run<br />\n<br />\n負皮- 守佢老母，用「光復香港，時代革命」呢句口號，音波攻擊震撚死啲狗"},{"pid":"9ec0c69adf5a7b280a5a1f56d5b391fc9dc1493d","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"對我黎講，「光復香港，時代革命」絕對唔只係一句口號，大家自己諗下"},{"pid":"6ece17fa4e5feb8dbb8a518e92dbf0640b6dccd9","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:24:18.000Z","msg":"再有更多手足比人拉只會令44位義士被告暴動嘅focus shift左<br />\n<br />\n義士唔係condom啊"},{"pid":"c97858e3d77ef7e32bb2aba5b24b0dff594946c6","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山狗屋同今日紅隧嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">hit and run</span></span> 絕對令大家士氣大增，你班撚樣同意嗎？"},{"pid":"02449aa94bbd1d7be4e45e0a27b57350dde72166","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"定你地所謂嘅前線想show自己有幾咁勇武，然後連累更多同路人比人拉啊？"},{"pid":"d2c318b85410a332999849783bafed62d4f4647b","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"你地或者可以拼左條命上前線頂，我好感激你地，但好多同路人企到咁前都會驚架。<br />\n<br />\n但我地又唔可以dum低你地。<br />\n<br />\n但無謂嘅死守同對峙會令更多想齊上齊落嘅手足比人拉啊！"},{"pid":"f56525905c660a20629492e8bbb639ea4ee0a427","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:35:07.000Z","msg":"我地可以為前線勇武一齊上，但你地可唔可以為左我地一齊落啊？"},{"pid":"b3f634db8eb51c060bab67a8728a33db7b2260f9","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"我唔想呢個階段再有無謂嘅犧牲啊"},{"pid":"6a5ca1d767bb782d9743ce9717e926f6f6adeb50","tid":1402941,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff26521bcb56f98e1fc60c1e090e75e3965a59f","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:39:15.000Z","msg":"其實今日有個我識嘅女生比狗捉左⋯⋯"},{"pid":"ed311a75f45231417e864e06c3d6182c75dd9a3a","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:43:38.000Z","msg":"聽日有冇人一齊去屌鳩前線死守前線？<br />\n東西兩邊一齊屌"},{"pid":"cc98c6d8c3df3f0c45ae4e585629a1578d614db7","tid":1402941,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:45:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2ea291a88fa45712111f91ab2a8580b1320342a","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣野好撚重要，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Scout嘅資訊其實好有用</span><br />\n<br />\n知道啲狗咩位黎，你班撚樣咪睇完就算，然後企定定等比狗咬啦！"},{"pid":"a19d950155072ad03c71f46c7710892f2991a253","tid":1402941,"uid":15362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b2ea291a88fa45712111f91ab2a8580b1320342a","tid":1402941,"uid":42943,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"仲有一樣野好撚重要，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Scout嘅資訊其實好有用</span><br />\n<br />\n知道啲